General.Name: Doxa AB
General.Description: Doxa AB (publ) focuses on real estate investments in Sweden and internationally. Its property portfolio includes commercial and residential properties, offices, hotel and conferences, sports and event arena, and warehouse and light industrial properties. The company also acquires, owns, builds, and manages housing properties. Doxa AB (publ) was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in Malmo, Sweden.
